Company Overview of Edgemoor Investment Advisors, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Edgemoor Investment Advisors, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides wealth management services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, retirement plans, trusts, charitable organizations, and foundations, investment companies, and pension and profit sharing plans. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity mutual fund for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm invests in value stocks to create its equity portfolios. For fixed income investments, it invests in...
Edgemoor Investment Advisors, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides wealth management services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, retirement plans, trusts, charitable organizations, and foundations, investment companies, and pension and profit sharing plans. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity mutual fund for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm invests in value stocks to create its equity portfolios. For fixed income investments, it invests in government and corporate bonds, senior corporate notes, utilities, REITs, and other high dividend stocks, preferred stocks, master limited partnerships, and income trusts. The firm employs fundamental analysis to make its investments. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. Edgemoor Investment Advisors, Inc. was founded in 1999 and is based in Bethesda, Maryland.
